{"synckey":1693453903,"updated":[{"bookId":"3300051132","bookmarkId":"3300051132_96_3093-3341","createTime":1693453903,"chapterUid":96,"colorStyle":2,"type":1,"markText":"200多年过去了，马尔萨斯的理论——两条公理下的三行小“程序”：富则生，穷则死，人多就穷[插图]——已是几乎所有科学家思考历史的基本框架。","range":"3093-3341"},{"bookId":"3300051132","bookmarkId":"3300051132_96_2316-2407","createTime":1693453865,"chapterUid":96,"colorStyle":2,"type":1,"markText":"所谓富种起源之谜，其实是两个谜叠加在一起。1800年以前，人类为什么穷？1800年之后，人类是怎么变富的？其中第一个谜又是第二个谜的基础。不理解一开始为什么穷，就无从理解后来的转折。","range":"2316-2407"},{"bookId":"3300051132","bookmarkId":"3300051132_96_1897-1921","createTime":1693453744,"chapterUid":96,"colorStyle":2,"type":1,"markText":"营养匮乏使男性平均身高停留在160厘米甚至更矮。","range":"1897-1921"},{"bookId":"3300051132","bookmarkId":"3300051132_96_1041-1102","createTime":1693453728,"chapterUid":96,"colorStyle":2,"type":1,"markText":"如果把外星人的第一个问题称作“物种起源之谜”，那么我们不妨把第二个问题称作“富种起源之谜”：人类，这个物种，是怎么变富的？","range":"1041-1102"},{"bookId":"3300051132","bookmarkId":"3300051132_96_971-1012","createTime":1693453720,"chapterUid":96,"colorStyle":2,"type":1,"markText":"如果一个星球上的生产力爆炸已经启动，享受其成果的智慧生命理解这一切是如何发生的吗？","range":"971-1012"}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"前言","chapterUid":96,"chapterIdx":6}],"book":{"bookId":"3300051132","version":619166935,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/73/cpplatform_1kwuyjmy1gzejmckvspjms/s_cpplatform_1kwuyjmy1gzejmckvspjms1677837448.jpg","title":"富种起源：人类是怎么变富的","author":"吴乐旻","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"K6R{lNt7_N$*fiShxuayWB","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#1f1c18"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#1f1c18"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#1f1c18"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#34302c"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#34302c"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#34302c"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#4b4742"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#4b4742"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#4b4742"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#4b4742"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#645f5a"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#645f5a"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#645f5a"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#7d7973"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#7d7973"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#7